; Regression test for issue #1607: Make timeclock transactions balanced (BZ#535)
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/1607
;
; When a bucket account is configured, timeclock transactions (i/o entries)
; should create balanced double-entry postings with a second posting against
; the bucket account.

bucket Equity:Time

i 2013/03/28 10:00:00 Projects:Consulting
o 2013/03/28 14:00:00

test bal
              -4.00h  Equity:Time
               4.00h  Projects:Consulting
--------------------
                   0
end test

test reg
13-Mar-28                       Projects:Consulting           4.00h        4.00h
                                Equity:Time                  -4.00h            0
end test
